    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Letters on Roman and Byzantine coins indicating the particular workshop of a mint that produced the coins; used from the mid-3rd century to the early 8th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
